data.title: The Jesuit Schools Network promotes the educational ministry of the Society of Jesus in service to the Catholic Church by strengthening Jesuit schools for the mission of Jesus Christ.
data.text:
Welcome to the Jesuit Schools Network

As part of the Jesuit Conference of Canada and the United States, we provide programming and support to 91 secondary and pre-secondary schools, our Member Schools. As a member of the Jesuit Global Network of Schools, collaboration is at the core of our work as we partner with Jesuit schools across the globe. Our mission is to animate the educational ministry of the Society of Jesus in Canada, the United States, Belize, and Micronesia in service of the Catholic Church by strengthening Jesuit schools for the mission of Jesus Christ.
